{"tid":1127472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"驚！子瑜雙腿大開洩春光 一個動作讓粉絲心疼暴怒了","createTime":"2019-04-27T06:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T06:50:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":172,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd7ecca950cd4e71e0ec3b87ab342d3b915312e","tid":1127472,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"〔記者翁子涵／台北報導〕南韓人氣女團TWICE，日前推出新專輯《FANCY YOU》回歸歌壇，有別以以往青春洋溢的甜美風格，這次她們大展性感風格，台籍成員子瑜還在新歌預告影片中穿極短皮裙，開衩開衩到大腿根部，昨（25）晚她們參加音樂節目《M！Countdown》宣傳新曲時，卻因裙子過短加上舞蹈動作較大，多數成員的安全褲不慎外洩，讓粉絲相當火大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/26/2771892_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F2771892_1.jpg&h=6bd1df11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE新造型火辣。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/26/2771892_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F2771892_2.jpg&h=e55ed8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE底褲外洩。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/26/2771892_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F2771892_3.jpg&h=29f4d86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜（右一）黑底褲也露出。（翻攝自YouTube））<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/26/2771892_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F2771892_4.jpg&h=2331d175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜（右一）還趁空檔把裙子往下拉。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n昨晚TWICE登上音樂節目《M！Countdown》表演新歌，成員分別穿著繽紛的打歌服，更有7位成員穿上了膝上迷你裙，熱舞過程中恰好有不少蹲下以及開腿的動作，鏡頭拍攝角度又是由下往上，讓不少成員在表演時，安全褲全都露，連子瑜的黑底褲都被看光光，跳到一半她還趕緊把裙子往下拉，讓大批粉絲紛紛痛罵「裙子真的太短了，不知道造型師在幹嘛」、「這可以告攝影師性騷擾了吧」。"},{"pid":"be306173a2911d19a75f4a757f2751dbeec74ab5","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":85,"dislike":58,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42de93bb0ec33503bae89dcbc48f12c3d29897c2","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":67,"dislike":40,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89516a3f8a2c1bee6ec6ee522423b2469c2bffb5","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":154,"dislike":6,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5e18d4f59819fc3f84ea85eb49ef69dd038cc5c","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e693a3dacbdd0ba30e139dc05978ffad8c2c92de","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f24ed9c0b1cc22b2dddea75f263f58258032d41c","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55309848dacff4a926332662c84ec6e9941516bd","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64497baad6b769e2db1255cb9b0d69d041f90e7e","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c364a36312984a13f6cd22889518abc1a437dcc2","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce9776839d38ce187857dc9e5dd74b007e635084","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":9,"dislike":22,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cdee6cf9307c740ee166fe3341ce31b425d627f","tid":1127472,"uid":76098,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"冇留言既 做乜撚"},{"pid":"4f486100da12ba651d063a4b7f2209f423bd4656","tid":1127472,"uid":223790,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T0